### Register New User
# @name register
POST {{MovieAppPortfolio_HostAddress}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Save Token from Registration
